{"tid":332273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(蝻vs犬）尼籍漢老蘭追打途人襲警　警犬鎮壓擒人　","createTime":"2017-07-23T00:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T02:00:22.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb25c5f2915802ab2b39676bfbd72e04f0bf5c9","tid":332273,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T00:36:49.000Z","msg":"中環尼籍漢蒲老蘭「發酒癲」追打途人兼襲警，被警犬鎮壓咬傷就擒。今晨4時許，一名身有酒氣的尼泊爾男子，與2名友人在蘭桂坊消遣，期間酒後失常見人就打，多名途人遇襲。一名警長及一名攜同警犬的警員巡經，見狀上前制止，惟警長遭人襲擊，身旁警犬見勢上前向尼泊爾男手部噬咬，尼漢友人趁亂逃去。大批警員趕至增援，並將尼漢制服，他涉嫌襲警被捕，由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170723/mobile/bkn-20170723054742078-0723_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170723%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170723054742078-0723_00822_001.html&d=mxJ%2BkpG7EZ%2F21TUAh2xXpbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=5f380340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170723/mobile/bkn-20170723054742078-0723_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/083627_849100d302a107481cdc2b3a7d8dfb75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F083627_849100d302a107481cdc2b3a7d8dfb75.jpg&h=c42cc91f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35a84d35abed77463a647feb75502e2b61713ddd","tid":332273,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T00:40:06.000Z","msg":"應該修例<br />\n非華人係香港鬧事可以headshot"},{"pid":"0e374ca411d9d50da4fd4871e564b4786f31c019","tid":332273,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T00:40:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又係蝻</span></span>"},{"pid":"2c43dc868b566e8d0b5b1b6e2680c69a3b9995a4","tid":332273,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T00:40:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該修例<br />\n非華人係香港鬧事可以headshot</blockquote>平時覺得你on9<br />\n今次都忍唔住認同你"},{"pid":"ad8c2c